Class FileBrowserDialog.FileButton

  • java.lang.Object
    • vialab.SMT.PGraphicsDelegate
      • vialab.SMT.Zone
        • ca.uwaterloo.epad.ui.FileBrowserDialog.FileButton
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.awt.event.KeyListener, java.util.EventListener, processing.core.PConstants
    Enclosing class:
    FileBrowserDialog

    public class FileBrowserDialog.FileButton
extends vialab.SMT.Zone
    This class represents a single item in the list of files in the file browser. Image files are displayed as thumbnails, save files generated by ePad application have thumbnails as well, all other files are displayed as text (path to the file).
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Dmitry Pyryeskin
